1.4.name: wordpress/cmb
1.4.description:
Colour Me Bad is a little app in Action Script that takes information from your recent played tracks in Last FM , picks up the top tags for that music and cross searches that with Kuler’s tags, resulting in a graphic representation of your music and , some would argue, your mood. I am planning to develop this into all kind of other directions, anyone out there who is feeling the direction i am going with this and would like to collaborate please hit me on the contact page and hopefully we can get rich and creative.
